imdb.plot outline: Your biggest dream is to perform on stage with real stars? You want to play an act in one of the most favored TV series? There is a big skateboarding event and you want to show what you can? Make your dream come true! In each episode of CN Durchstarter a kid is facing a challenge that is asking a lot of the children but never too much. They have a realistic chance of breaking the task and making their dream come true by gritting their teeth and demonstrating discipline and ambition. Each challenge is completed with a big performance at a popular real-life event. All children are being coached by Detlef D! Soost who is popular host of the long running casting show "Popstars" (Pop Idol). He is accompanying the kids on their journey, pushing and motivating them. The show is about a sense of achievement, team spirit and making new friends. The aim is to boost the child's confidence and self-esteem and to show them that they can reach their goals if they really believe in them.
